00:05:38,333 --> 00:05:40,333
Saya ada seorang kawan...

63
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,200
Pulanglah!

64
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:18,733
Tuan,

65
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:20,600
