66
00:06:20,633 --> 00:06:21,600
Seorang lelaki

67
00:06:22,533 --> 00:06:23,799
sepatutnya mengaku cintanya terlebih dahulu.

68
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,333
Sebelum saya berjumpa denganmu,

69
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,666
